/T%E1%BA%A1m-s%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%B4-d%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1t-T%C3%A2n-L%C3%A2m-ch%C3%AD-Kinh-%E1%BA%A4p-t%E1%BA%B7ng-t%C3%A2y/poem-etQGdYZboCBIAn3juqZLhA">Tạm sứ Hạ Đô dạ phát Tân Lâm chí Kinh Ấp tặng tây - 暫使下都夜發新林至京邑贈西</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Di%E1%BB%85u/author-fi0AnZEbTlY085rk8ctF-w">Tạ Diễu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/Tr%C3%A0/poem-LD3vA-WExVKONEFMdna0RQ">Trà - 茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/author-LbaVSB66mX6k1U09t5TO2A">Lâm Bô</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Tuy%C3%AAn-Ch%C3%A2u-T%E1%BA%A1-Di%E1%BB%85u-l%C3%A2u-ti%E1%BB%85n-bi%E1%BB%87t-hi%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0-th%C3%BAc-V%C3%A2n/poem-03Ril1g6U9fK37IjTxDE9w">Tuyên Châu Tạ Diễu lâu tiễn biệt hiệu thư thúc Vân - 宣州謝眺樓餞別校書叔雲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/V%C3%A2n-L%C3%A2m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-DjZPTzDjQ3uLEVgSMtDeUQ">Vân Lâm Nguyễn tướng quân - 雲林阮將軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/author-aojK5yt7X8rTWmkDYWXgEg">Trần Huy Liễn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
